29 classrooms and each public kindergarten classroom to
30 implement the guidelines and training requirements.
31 This bill would also require DHR to oversee the
32 implementation of this act for licensed child-care
33 facilities, the Secretary of the Department of Early
34 Childhood Education for prekindergarten classrooms, and
35 local boards of education for kindergarten classrooms.
