38 A BILL
39 TO BE ENTITLED
40 AN ACT
41
42 Relating to early childhood education; to add Article
43 4, commencing with Section 26-24-40, to Chapter 24, Title 26,
44 and Sections 16-40-15 and 38-7-7.1 to the Code of Alabama
45 1975; to require the Department of Early Childhood Education
46 to develop guidelines and training for appropriate screen time
47 use in early childhood education settings; to provide limits
48 on the use of screen time in licensed child-care facilities,
49 certain prekindergarten classrooms, and public kindergarten
50 classrooms; to require certain teachers and staff members to
51 annually undergo training; to require the Department of Early
52 Childhood Education, the Department of Human Resources, and
53 the State Board of Education to implement the guidelines and
54 training requirements for the early childhood education
55 programs under their jurisdiction; to condition licensure of
56 child-care facilities on compliance with screen time
